---
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../components/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Ron Keesing | Enterprise AI"
  description="Enterprise AI Strategy, Trusted AI Governance, and Human-Centered AI Transformation."
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <section class="introduction">
      <div class="site-container">
        <div class="thesis">
          <p>
            Enterprise AI transformation requires deep technical understanding.
          </p>

          <p>
            It also demands strategy, governance, and disciplined execution.
          </p>

          <p>
            And it only succeeds when people remain at the center.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="accent-rule" aria-hidden="true"></div>

        <p class="grounding">
          Those views are grounded in my experience building and deploying AI
          in complex, real-world environments where trust, performance, and
          reliability are essential. They reflect my approach to leading AI
          change that allows organizations to solve their most important
          challenges in new ways, creating new capabilities while delivering
          measurable value.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="leadership site-container"
      id="executive-leadership"
      aria-labelledby="leadership-heading"
    >
      <SectionHeader
        title="Executive Leadership"
        id="leadership-heading"
      />

      <div class="leadership-list">
        <article class="leadership-item">
          <h3>First Chief AI Officer</h3>

          <p>
            Built and led the enterprise AI capability for a Fortune 300
            technology company.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="leadership-item">
          <h3>Enterprise AI Strategy</h3>

          <p>
            Led three successive generations of enterprise AI strategy as the
            technology evolved from machine learning to generative and agentic
            AI.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="leadership-item">
          <h3>Trusted AI Governance</h3>

          <p>
            Designed and scaled enterprise AI governance for adoption across
            highly regulated, mission-critical organizations.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article class="leadership-item">
          <h3>Business Impact</h3>

          <p>
            Led AI initiatives that generated more than 
            <strong>$50 million</strong> in direct annual business impact while
            enabling <strong>billions of dollars</strong> in new business.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .introduction {
    padding: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.5rem) 0
      clamp(3.5rem, 5.5vw, 5rem);
  }

  .thesis {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
  }

  .thesis p {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: none;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 2.45vw, 2.4rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.018em;
  }

  .accent-rule {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2px;
    margin: 2.2rem 0 1.9rem;
    background: var(--accent);
  }

  .grounding {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.3vw, 1.1rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .leadership {
    padding-bottom: clamp(4rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
  }

  .leadership-list {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .leadership-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(240px, 0.8fr) minmax(0, 1.55fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
    padding: 1.8rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .leadership-item h3 {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 2vw, 1.65rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
  }

  .leadership-item p {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: clamp(0.98rem, 1.35vw, 1.08rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .leadership-item strong {
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .leadership-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0.55rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .thesis p {
      font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 7vw, 2.1rem);
    }
  }
</style>

